Hi, Li,

Please create the file "~/.R/Makevars" and put the following content in it

CC=clang-omp
CXX=clang-omp++
CFLAGS += -O3 -Wall -pipe -pedantic
CXXFLAGS += -O3 -Wall -pipe -Wno-unused -pedantic -fopenmp

You can add or change flags in this file.

Best,

KK

